rows.label: qst200311_msg0002
rows.name:
Ran right into it at the
main gate of Teos Aure.

rows.label: qst200311_msg0003
rows.name:
Ah, I'm fine. It didn't do anything,
just ran out of the city.

rows.label: qst200311_msg0008
rows.name:
If you can find its footprints,
you should be able to follow it.

rows.label: qst200311_msg0004
rows.name:
But you know, Gogols are
gentle-natured monsters.

rows.label: qst200311_msg0006
rows.name:
It must be because Luxuria ended its
isolation and people started digging
salt caves all over the place...

rows.label: qst200311_msg0007
rows.name:
I bet it got scared and wandered
into the city by mistake.
